---
import SectionLayout from './SectionLayout.astro';
import { LINKEDIN_URL } from '../../lib/constants';
---

<SectionLayout bgColor="grey" extraStyles="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Meet the Author</h2>
  <img
    src="/foto_cv.jpeg"
    alt="The author Irene Mateo Herrero"
    class="mx-auto mt-6 w-40 h-40 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg text-center"
  />
  <p class="mt-4 mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-4 md:px-8">
    <b>Irene Mateo Herrero</b> is a passionate <b
      >full-stack developer and mentor</b
    >, who transitioned from teaching to the tech industry. With years of
    experience navigating the challenges of teaching and mentorship, <b
      >she has helped numerous individuals achieve their career goals</b
    >. Irene's unique journey, from the classroom to the world of software
    development, has shaped her approach to mentorship, making it <b
      >accessible, relatable, and practical</b
    > for anyone seeking to grow in their careers.
  </p>
  <div class="flex justify-center">
    <a
      href={LINKEDIN_URL}
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 text-center"
    >
      LinkedIn
    </a>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>
